<Main title="Servers - pwned.page">
    <section>
        <h1>Our Infrastructure</h1>
        <p>
            At Pwned.page, we prioritize independence and strive to minimize
            reliance on cloud services, ensuring greater control and security.
        </p>

        <h2>Physical Server</h2>
        <p>
            The physical server serves as the core infrastructure for
            Pwned.page. It runs hardened NixOS on TMPFS, handling the majority
            of the site's operations.
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <strong>Processor:</strong> Intel Pentium G4560 (2 cores, 4 threads)
            </li>
            <li><strong>Memory:</strong> 16 GB DDR4</li>
            <li>
                <strong>Storage:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>128 GB NVMe SSD</li>
                    <li>256 GB SATA SSD</li>
                    <li>1 TB HDD (RAID 1)</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Network Connectivity:</strong> 1 Gbps Ethernet</li>
            <li><strong>Operating System:</strong> NixOS</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Virtual Private Server (VPS)</h2>
        <p>
            The VPS is dedicated to hosting the email server for Pwned.page,
            ensuring reliable communication infrastructure.
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <strong>Processor:</strong> Intel Xeon E5-2680 v2 (1 core, 1 thread)
            </li>
            <li><strong>Memory:</strong> 1 GB DDR4</li>
            <li><strong>Storage:</strong> 10 GB SSD</li>
            <li><strong>Network Connectivity:</strong> 1 Gbps Ethernet</li>
            <li>
                <strong>Operating System:</strong> Ubuntu Server 22.04.5 LTS
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Data Center Location:</strong> New York, United States
            </li>
        </ul>
    </section>
</Main>
